    "Title": "Missing: ~mission(TargetName)",
    "Description": "One of our people, ~mission(TargetName), was supposed to be doing some preliminary scouting work over at ~mission(Location|Address), but they never reported in. We\u2019re hoping that they just ran into some bad luck, but too often out here even the smallest misstep can prove fatal.\n\nI\u2019d appreciate someone heading that way and seeing if they can be located. It\u2019d be great if you find them alive, but if not, some closure is the least we can do for their family.\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
